title.narrative: Relevant MDAs and select LGAs and communities have enhanced capacities to deliver quality and relevant formal basic education

description.narrative: A nation-wide dissemination of results of the national early grade assessment of learning outcomes was completed, engaging all 26 Regional Education Officers, 26 Regional Academic Officers and 186 District Education Officers. Additionally, a Library-in-a box initiative was introduced in Mbeya and Njombe regions, further strengthening parental engagement in supporting their children’s learning at home, benefiting 7,492 pre-primary and standards I and II learners (3,874 boys, 3,618 girls). | Status:Partially met | As-of Date:20/12/2021
